The finer details  
 

Men and women at Peabody 
Across our organisation, women are slightly less well represented than men, making 
up 46% of our workforce. While women are well represented at the higher levels of 
the organisation, our lowest paid band is 74% male.  

Percentage of men and women at Peabody

